{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "12c0fdb7-b740-475f-b04f-1727bb155d46", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/12c0fdb7-b740-475f-b04f-1727bb155d46@2.pkg/1772597483992/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597485125", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/12c0fdb7-b740-475f-b04f-1727bb155d46@2.pkg/1772597483992/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597485125"}, "identifier": "12c0fdb7-b740-475f-b04f-1727bb155d46", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①：村民共同协商制定村规民约，体现了协商民主在基层治理中的作用，故①说法符合题意；②：村民自治直接管理的是本村公共事务，间接管理国家事务，故②说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>③：民主管理是人民行使民主权利的方式之一，但公民的基本政治权利是选举权和被选举权，故③说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>④：村规民约由村民会议制定，属于基层群众自治的体现，符合基层群众自治制度的要求，故①说法符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）某村公示的《小公约》由社区居民委员会牵头，通过线上征集意见、线下居民议事会等多轮讨论后共同制定，涵盖了垃圾分类、宠物管理、公共空间维护等社区日常事务。这份“大家事、大家议、大家建、大家管”的&nbsp;“小公约” 的制定（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①彰显了社会主义协商民主的独特优势&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ②有利于该村村民直接管理国家事务</p>\n\n<p>③体现民主管理是公民的基本政治权利&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ④体现了我国坚持基层群众自治制度</p>\n", "title": "（原创）某村公示的《小公约》由社区居民委员会牵头，通过线上征集意见、线下居民议事会等多轮讨论后共同制定，涵盖了垃圾分类、宠物管理、公共空间维护等社区日常事务。这份“大家事、大家议、大家建、大家管”的 “小公约” 的制定（   ）①彰显了社会主义协商民主的独特优势      ②有利于该村村民直接管理国家事务③体现民主管理是公民的基本政治权利      ④体现了我国坚持基层群众自治制度", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/12c0fdb7-b740-475f-b04f-1727bb155d46@2.pkg/item.json?v=1754819670872", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（原创）某村公示的《小公约》由社区居民委员会牵头，通过线上征集意见、线下居民议事会等多轮讨论后共同制定，涵盖了垃圾分类、宠物管理、公共空间维护等社区日常事务。这份“大家事、大家议、大家建、大家管”的&nbsp;“小公约” 的制定（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①彰显了社会主义协商民主的独特优势&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ②有利于该村村民直接管理国家事务</p>\n\n<p>③体现民主管理是公民的基本政治权利&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ④体现了我国坚持基层群众自治制度</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], 